timeOffset: 1.1, type: \"info\", text: \"Synchronized state records for RetailMesh and OreMesh deployments.\" },\n290 |       { timeOffset: 1.9, type: \"agent\", text: \"[TelemetryAgent] Aggregating daily transaction throughput: $14.8M reconciled, normal limits.\" },\n291 |       { timeOffset: 2.6, type: \"agent\", text: \"[OutlierAgent] Identified atypical database activity spikes in European node between 03:00-03:15 UTC.\" },\n292 |       { timeOffset: 3.3, type: \"info\", text: \"[OutlierAgent] Spike resolved to standard system backup routine. No active threat.\" },\n293 |       { timeOffset: 4.0, type: \"agent\", text: \"[EditorialModel] Formatting executive brief: Focus areas, Revenue stability, Operational alerts.\" },\n294 |       { timeOffset: 4.6, type: \"success\", text: \"Brief compiled, encrypted, and synchronized. Delivery secure.\" }\n295 |     ]\n296 |   },\n297 |   {\n298 |     id: \"compliance-assistant\",\n299 |     name: \"Sovereign Regulatory Compliance Auditor\",\n300 |     category: \"Compliance Assistant\",\n301 |     purpose: \"Monitors active database migrations and system modifications for PII leaks, storage location violations, and rule breaches.\",\n302 |     recommendedIndustry: \"Government & Sovereign\",\n303 |     relatedPlatform: \"Assessment Mesh / Auditor\",\n304 |     agentType: \"Guardrail / Audit\",\n305 |     status: \"Enclave Verified\",\n306 |     securityRating: \"Military-Grade Secure\",\n307 |     metrics: {\n308 |       cpu: \"16-Core vCPU\",\n309 |       memory: \"64GB Isolated\",\n310 |       isolation: \"AMD SEV-SNP\",\n311 |       compliance: \"GDPR / HIPAA / FedRAMP\"\n312 |     },\n313 |     ingressLabel: \"Database Config & Commits\",\n314 |     egressLabel: \"Compliance Block / Approval\",\n315 |     steps: [\n316 |       {\n317 |         title: \"Boundary Scanning\",\n318 |         description: \"Scans new code commits, schema files, and storage bucket descriptors for geopolitical regulatory alignment.\",\n319 | 