                      <div key={idx} className=\"relative group\">\n1028 |                             \n1029 |                             {/* Step chron node badge */}\n1030 |                             <div className=\"absolute -left-[21px] top-1.5 w-[11px] h-[11px] rounded-full bg-black border-2 border-[#009DFF] flex items-center justify-center z-10\">\n1031 |                               <div className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF]/60\" />\n1032 |                             </div>\n1033 | \n1034 |                             <div className=\"space-y-1 pl-4\">\n1035 |                               <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n1036 |                                 <span className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-white\">\n1037 |                                   Step {idx + 1}: {step.title}\n1038 |                                 </span>\n1039 |                                 <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-white/40 uppercase\">\n1040 |                                   {step.role}\n1041 |                                 </span>\n1042 |                               </div>\n1043 |                               <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 font-light leading-relaxed\">\n1044 |                                 {step.description}\n1045 |                               </p>\n1046 |                             </div>\n1047 |                           </div>\n1048 |                         ))}\n1049 |                       </div>\n1050 |                     </div>\n1051 |                   )}\n1052 | \n1053 |                   {activeTab === \"architecture\" && (\n1054 |                     <div className=\"space-y-6 flex flex-col h-full\">\n1055 |                       <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n1056 |                         <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider block font-bold\">FLOW TOPOLOGY ARCHITECTURE</span>\n1057 |                         <h4 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Isolated Data Routing & Cryptographic DAG</h4>\n1058 |                         <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 font-light\">\n1059 |                           Cryptographic verification and decryption happen natively at physical memory boundary nodes. No data touches raw external servers.\n1060 |                         </p>\n1061 |                       </div>\n1062 | \n1063 |                       {/* DYNAMIC SVG CANVAS */}\n1064 |                       <div className=\"p-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden\">\n1065 |                         {renderSVGArchitecture(activeAgent)}\n1066 |                       </div>\n1067 |                     </div>\n1068 |                   )}\n1069 | \n1070 |                   {activeTab === \"security\" && (\n1071 |                     <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n1072 |                       <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n1073 |                         <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-wider block font-bold\">GOVERNANCE METRICS</span>\n1074 |                         <h4 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Platform Alignment & Compliance Guardrails</h4>\n1075 |                         <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 font-light\">\n1076 |                           This deployment configuration is validated using static binary checks and certified against global privacy rules.\n1077 |                         </p>\n1078 |                       </div>\n1079 | \n1080 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n1081 |                         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] space-y-2\">\n1082 |                           <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider block font-bold\">SOVEREIGN TRUST RATING</span>\n1083 |                           <p className=\"text-xs text-white/80 font-light\">\n1084 |                             Fully compliant under sovereign regional regulation patterns. Hardware enclaves lock memory access keys dynamically.\n1085 |                           </p>\n1086 |                         </div>\n1087 |                         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] space-y-2\">\n1088 |                           <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider block font-bold\">ZERO-TRUST AUDIT LOGS</span>\n1089 |                           <p className=\"text-xs text-white/80 font-light\">\n1090 |                             Immutable logging layer writes SHA-256 block receipts for each transaction without persisting PII attributes locally.\n1091 |                           </p>\n1092 |                         </div>\n1093 |                         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] space-y-2\">\n1094 |                           <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-wider block font-bold\">MODEL DRIFT GUARD</span>\n1095 |                           <p className=\"text-xs text-white/80 font-light\">\n1096 |                             Continuous compliance score filters and mitigates potential hallucination patterns down to less than 0.01% standard.\n1097 |                           </p>\n1098 |                         </div>\n1099 |                         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] space-y-2\">\n1100 |                           <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-wider block font-bold\">VIRTUAL PRIVATE CANOPY</span>\n1101 |                           <p className=\"text-xs text-white/80 font-light\">\n1102 |                             Isolated VPC boundary blockages deny any unencrypted internet egress during agent transaction routing tasks.\n1103 |                           </p>\n1104 |            