undry Studio\" (href: `/build/foundry-studio`). I'm now verifying the layout.\n\n\n**Analyzing Sandbox Imports**\n\nI'm now analyzing the size of `/app/build/sandbox/page.tsx`, focusing on a clean rewrite. I've noted the imported libraries, specifically `motion/react`, which is now available thanks to the successful build. I am verifying that the existing components (`InnerPageShell`, `InnerPageHero`, `PremiumCTA`, and `MotionReveal`) are utilized without breaking anything. I'm focusing on crafting high-fidelity mock data for the eight agents, ensuring a custom experience, and preparing the updated `AGENTS` array.\n\n\n**Drafting Agent Data**\n\nI'm now drafting the updated code for `/app/build/sandbox/page.tsx`, and plan to replace the existing content with this new draft. First, I verified the existing `AGENTS` array. There are indeed 8 agents. I'm focused on meticulously crafting complete, specific data for all eight agents. I've drafted agent properties including: `id`, `name`, `category`, `purpose`, `recommendedIndustry`, `relatedPlatform`, `agentType`, `status`, `securityRating`, and `metrics`. I am verifying the data.\n\n\n**Defining Agent Isolation**\n\nI'm now incorporating detailed isolation properties within the agent data. I've added crucial elements to each agent's profile. Specifically, I'm defining parameters for each agent, including: \"64GB Isolated\", \"isolation\": \"AMD SEV-SNP\", and \"compliance\": \"Sovereign GDPR\". I'm meticulously detailing their security posture.\n\nI'm now drafting the updated code for `/app/build/sandbox/page.tsx`, and plan to replace the existing content with this new draft. First, I verified the existing `AGENTS` array. There are indeed 8 agents. I'm focused on meticulously crafting complete, specific data for all eight agents. I've drafted agent properties including: `id`, `name`, `category`, `purpose`, `recommendedIndustry`, `relatedPlatform`, `agentType`, `status`, `securityRating`, and `metrics`. I am verifying the